OL,3,C19 amendments proposed to Guernsey's
OL,4,C2025 budget
OL,6,FAnalysis by ITV Channel's reporter
OL,7,FMatthew Leach:
OL,9,F19 amendments to the budget, mainly
OL,10,Frepeating a handful of well worn
OL,11,Farguments and debates.
OL,13,FIt's almost as if there's an election
OL,14,Faround the corner.
OL,16,FUnless Policy and Resources alters its
OL,17,Fown budget or brings forward some kind
OL,18,Fof consolidation amendment, the debate
OL,19,Fon the 5 November is going to be a
OL,20,Flong one.
