OL,6,FAnd it's not just the headlines. Yes,
OL,7,Fwe'll be discussing the ever
OL,8,Fcontroversial GST package alongside a
OL,9,Fpossible increase in income tax by 2p
OL,10,Fon the pound, and corporate tax
OL,11,Freform, but there are several chunky
OL,12,Ftopics buried in the other amendments
OL,13,Ftoo.
OL,15,FDeputy Peter Roffey wants to exempt
OL,16,Ffood from a possible GST, and his
OL,17,FCommittee - Employment and Social
OL,18,FSecurity - wants extra money for
OL,19,Fsocial housing maintenance.
